    given-names: Mohammed Akbar
    affiliation: "Independent Researcher"
    country: IN
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/mohammedakbaransari/glassbox-agentic-governance"
url: "https://github.com/mohammedakbaransari/glassbox-agentic-governance"
abstract: >
  GlassBox implements the decision-semantic layer — a runtime governance tier
  that intercepts every AI-generated operational decision before it reaches an
  enterprise execution system. Production-ready implementation validates, scores,
  routes, and audits decisions through a 9-stage pipeline with zero mandatory
  dependencies, full async support, SQLite-backed transactional storage,
  declarative rules, multi-tenancy, RAG governance, LangChain/LangGraph/AutoGen
  adapters, lock-pooling optimization (95% latency reduction), and comprehensive
  test coverage.
keywords:
